snippet.title: Journey to Foundation - Announce Trailer | PS5 Games
snippet.description:
A galactic spymaster is sent to infiltrate a group of defectors, only to uncover a dire truth that could change the course of their mission… and history.

Navigate a galaxy in chaos in Journey to Foundation, based on Isaac Asimov’s sci-fi epic, coming Fall 2023!

#ps5 #ps5games #stateofplay
